### GET all allergies for a patient
GET http://localhost:4000/patients/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000/allergies

###

### GET only active allergies for a patient
GET http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies/active

###

### GET severe allergies for a patient (critical for medical safety)
GET http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies/severe

###

### GET specific allergy by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies/{{allergy_id}}

###

### GET allergy count for a patient
GET http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies/count

###

### GET active allergy count for a patient
GET http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies/count/active

###
